$ NastAero VM2: Cantilever Beam Under End Moment
$ Reference: Timoshenko - Strength of Materials
$ 10 CBAR elements, L=10m, E=200GPa, I=1.0e-4 m^4
$ Applied moment M=10000 N-m at tip
$ Analytical: theta_tip = ML/EI = 10000*10/(200e9*1e-4) = 5.0e-3 rad
$ delta_tip = ML^2/(2EI) = 10000*100/(2*200e9*1e-4) = 2.5e-2 m
$
SOL 101
CEND
TITLE = VM2 - CANTILEVER BEAM UNDER END MOMENT
